snippet.title: Shelling Star gameplay
snippet.description:
Shelling Star is a simple missiles defense game that trained you reaction.

Inside game, missiles will come from surrounding, and aim to explode the fort.  The only one mission for you is to tap the screen to direct the auto-rotating fort to fire them and prevent them to close to the fort, otherwise, the fort will be exploded and game over.

Link:
IOS: 
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/Chasing/id1217702387?mt=8

Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sohk.shellingstar
